        "text": "Where a lot containing a cannabis production facility abuts a lot i. zoned or used for residential purposes, or ii. that is used for a daycare, community centre, school, religious institution, public park or playground, such facility, including any building or outdoor area used as a cannabis production facility, shall be set back a minimum 230 feet (70 metres) from the abutting lot line. OTHER REQUIREMENTS: CARETAKER UNITS",
